Your private photos and videos are stored only on your iPhone and never uploaded anywhere. This is the safest way to protect your privacy.
You can unlock the photo locker with your passcode or Face ID.

It’s one of the top-ranked photo vault apps in Japan.
Keep and revisit your favorite photos and videos with an app designed for privacy and simplicity.

Recommending Use of Secret Key Lock Album for:
- Keeping precious memories
- Storing private photos and protecting your privacy
- Creating personal collections
- Saving important information securely

What makes Secret Key Lock Album different?
• Clean, simple design with fast performance. Easy for anyone to use.
• All core features are available for free.
• If you need more storage, the in-app purchase is a one-time payment — no monthly fees or subscriptions.

Features:
- Instantly move your data with the auto-delete function.
- Supports videos, GIFs, Live Photos, Slo-mo, and Time-lapse, with a built-in video player.
- You can restore photos and videos back to the iPhone Photos app.
- Set any photo as your album cover.
- Saves photos in high resolution to keep your memories sharp.
- Add notes and comments to your important moments with the memo feature.
- Enjoy looking back on your memories with the built-in slideshow.
- Share photos and videos through AirDrop, social media, email, messages, and other supported apps.
- With Dropbox support, you can transfer your data wirelessly.

results.description:
Need to keep your photos, videos, and other files safe and secure? Secret Photo Vault Album is the best way to do it!

This incredible data manager and privacy locker lets you store everything from pictures to secret notes in an unbreakable security vault. Lock down photos from your camera, or record videos and keep them safe from nosy friends, all with unbeatable privacy and security you can rely on!

Best of all, Secret Photo Vault Album includes a powerful cloud storage sync feature that keeps all of your private data backed up and secure. You can even set unique lock options to increase the protection on your phone to keep intruders away!

Features Overview:
- Secure every photo, video, and note instantly.
- Set incredibly strong password locks.
- Keep all of your private data in one secure location.
- Manage passwords using the secure data locker.
- Reliable cloud back-up and photo synchronization service.

If you've got photos, videos, or notes you want to keep safe, or if you just need a reliable way to store private data in a secure vault locker, Secret Photo Vault Album is the best app for the job!

Secret Folder
- Move images and videos into a hidden vault to keep them out of sight from prying eyes.
- Only you can see your photos in this invisible location!

Cloud Transfers
- Cloud back-up features let you securely transfer content to a new device.

Media Storage & Sync
- Organize notes, videos, and photos into albums for easy viewing.
- Search and sort through content quickly and easily.
- Import and export photos and videos from your camera, photo albums, or cloud storage services like Dropbox and Google Drive.
- Unique photo filters let you add a personal touch to your pictures.
- Sync data across devices with ease.

Privacy
- Your data, photos, and files are accessible only by you!
- Switch active apps by flipping your device for instant privacy!
- Dummy screen protects your privacy even if a friend grabs your phone.
- If someone tries to access your data, take a selfie and record their location!
- Back up and restore content via iTunes and cloud storage.
- Compatible with Touch ID and Face ID.

It's time to keep your photos and videos safe from nosy friends! Download Secret Photo Vault Album now to lock up your private information with a safe and secure vault app that's easy (and fun) to use!

Secret Photo Vault Premium Subscription:
Secret Photo Vault Album offers several subscription choices of various duration and pricing. These packages include weekly ($4.99 USD), monthly ($9.99 USD), and yearly ($39.99 USD) package. You will be able to use more cloud storage, trash recovery, photo filter effects and more for the duration of subscription. 

Payment will be charged to iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase. Subscription automatically renews for the same price and duration period as the original "one week"/"one month"/"one year" package unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period. Account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period at the cost of the chosen package (weekly, monthly or yearly package). Subscriptions may be managed by the user and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the user's iTunes Account Settings after purchase. No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during active subscription period. You may cancel a subscription during its free trial period via the subscription setting through your iTunes account. This must be done 24 hours before the end of the subscription period to avoid being charged. You may turn off the auto-renewal of your subscription via your iTunes Account Settings. However, you are not able to cancel the current subscription during its active period. Unused portions of free trials will be forfeited upon purchase of a subscription. 

Privacy Policy: http://www.rvappstudios.com/app-privacy-policy.html
Terms of Use: http://www.rvappstudios.com/app-privacy-policy.html#terms/
